member.name: M:NumbatWallet.Domain.ValueObjects.Email.EmailValidationRegex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
^[a-zA-Z0-9.!#$%&'*+/=?^_`{|}~-]+@[a-zA-Z0-9](?:[a-zA-Z0-9-]{0,61}[a-zA-Z0-9])?(?:\\.[a-zA-Z0-9](?:[a-zA-Z0-9-]{0,61}[a-zA-Z0-9])?)*$
Options:
RegexOptions.Compiled
Explanation:
○ Match if at the beginning of the string.
○ Match a character in the set [!#-'*+--9=?A-Z^-~] atomically at least once.
○ Match '@'.
○ Match a character in the set [0-9A-Za-z].
○ Optional (greedy).
○ Match a character in the set [-0-9A-Za-z] greedily at most 61 times.
○ Match a character in the set [0-9A-Za-z].
○ Loop greedily any number of times.
○ Match '.'.
○ Match a character in the set [0-9A-Za-z].
○ Optional (greedy).
○ Match a character in the set [-0-9A-Za-z] greedily at most 61 times.
○ Match a character in the set [0-9A-Za-z].
○ Match if at the end of the string or if before an ending newline.

member.name: M:NumbatWallet.Domain.ValueObjects.PhoneNumber.PhoneValidationRegex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
^\\+\\d{7,15}$
Options:
RegexOptions.Compiled
Explanation:
○ Match if at the beginning of the string.
○ Match '+'.
○ Match a Unicode digit atomically at least 7 and at most 15 times.
○ Match if at the end of the string or if before an ending newline.
